		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/rendition-and-torture-interview-on-rtrt.html" title="Permalink to Rendition and torture — interview on RT" rel="bookmark">Rendition and torture — interview on <span class="caps">RT</span></a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/rendition-and-torture-interview-on-rtrt.html" title="15:50" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-12-19T15:50:34+00:00" pubdate>December 19, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
