		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here’s my recent inter­view on <span class="caps">RT</span>’s excel­lent and incis­ive new <span class="caps">UK</span> polit­ics pro­gramme, “<a href="http://rt.com/shows/going-underground/">Going Under­ground</a>”.  In it I dis­cuss rendi­tion, tor­ture, spy over­sight and much more:<br />
