		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/11/the-petraeus-affair.html" title="Permalink to The Petraeus Affair" rel="bookmark">The Petraeus Affair</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/11/the-petraeus-affair.html" title="20:33" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-11-14T20:33:22+00:00" pubdate>November 14, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/11/the-petraeus-affair.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My recent inter­view on <span class="caps">RT</span> about the Pet­raeus Affair and the pos­sible real reas­ons for his expos­ure and resignation:</p>
<p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/53486417" frameborder="0" width="500" height="281"></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/11/the-petraeus-affair.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/cia" title="View all posts in CIA" rel="category tag">CIA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/current-affairs" title="View all posts in Current Affairs" rel="category tag">Current Affairs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/fbi" title="View all posts in FBI" rel="category tag">FBI</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/interviews" title="View all posts in Interviews" rel="category tag">Interviews</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/iran" title="View all posts in Iran" rel="category tag">Iran</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/rttv" title="View all posts in RTTV" rel="category tag">RTTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/tv" title="View all posts in TV" rel="category tag">TV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/war-2" title="View all posts in War" rel="category tag">War</a>			</span>
